{"tid":498925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄女雙手被醋夫砍斷 另一隻手太碎駁唔返","createTime":"2017-12-14T08:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T10:19:38.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29a47e62150dd4ea04bb4a588836e1d2112b0f8c","tid":498925,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513156196_e463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513156196_e463.jpg&h=e42c779f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯莫斯科一名26歲男子聲稱妻子有外遇，一怒之下不理妻子否認，以斧頭殘暴斬碎她雙手手掌。妻子最後接受長達9小時的手術，但醫生盡了全力也只能為她駁回一隻手掌。<br />\n<br />\n格拉喬夫（Dmitry Grachyov）和妻子結婚5年，育有2名子女。他早前懷疑妻子有情夫後，某天將她帶到郊外拿出斧頭斬她手指企圖逼供，妻子解釋自己並無外遇，格拉喬夫則要求她接受測謊機測試，妻子亦同意，但他其後仍怒得不理妻子的話，猛然揮斧斬斷她2隻手掌。<br />\n男子犯案後並沒有潛逃，反駕車將妻子送院，自己向警方自首。醫諼人員隨即為其妻子進行歷時9小時的繁複手術，盡力將她的斷掌駁回。不幸地由於她的右手太碎傷勢太重，醫生只能為她駁回左掌，不過就留下多道駭人的傷痕。<br />\n主診醫生表示：「我們在下午6時50分開始（手術），凌晨3時50分才完成。我無法公開那些（女子雙手）原本的照片，那是血肉模糊的畫面，就連我也要控制好自己及有心理準備才能直視它們。這個案令我們都震驚，一個正常人做不出這樣的事。」<br />\n警方正徹查事件，格拉喬夫仍被拘留。據女方的親戚表示，格拉喬夫曾恐嚇妻子要殺了她，妻子亦曾報警求助，但警方其後只是找他問話了事。<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<br />\n左手<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513156195_6a96.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513156195_6a96.jpg&d=VgOsMrzToc1whm0geNSfczANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=d46c0fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513156195_6a96.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171214/57575777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57575777&d=VgOsMrzToc1whm0geNSfczANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=c3875dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57575777&h=48f31f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171214/57575777</a><br />\n<br />\n睇見都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afbc9308d0a06f1a9722b9636919f7ab2458fc1","tid":498925,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178760b328411bf60beca6037a6240cfdd218835","tid":498925,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"d俄佬個個都咁撚樣，好柒"},{"pid":"ff9dd4ebf0db94636bc70c250367969679744045","tid":498925,"uid":4696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"接受測謊機測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b752c79c0776a37b80219e05654443ceb89a8","tid":498925,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}